{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "平議生死", "storyInfo": "善良的明椒在混亂中給諾伯特區的薩卡茲酒店經理送去食物。Logos與變形者集群展開了關於文明與生存的辯論。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g1_glasgowboxinggym", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_throwstone", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_throwstone", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "false", "channel": "pen", "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 60.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別過來，你們別過來！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個瘦小的男人突然拿出了個什麼東西在空中揮舞著，是一支鋼筆，就算是在黑暗中，也能看清楚它上面的華貴裝飾。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位自稱能成為下個皇家科學院院士的紋章學家或許曾用它寫下不少精彩的考據。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而如今，它成了個可憐的，十足不體面的武器，被顫抖地握在掌中。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dropspanner", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-150", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "0,-150", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噹啷一聲，一個罐頭從男人的大衣裡滑落，男人慌忙彎腰撿起，又藏回自己的衣擺下。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先生，那是我們最後一個肉罐頭。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起。", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，我堅持不下去了。我快被逼瘋了！這片封鎖區，這些飄在空氣中的死人粉塵，這些屍體的臭味，這一切——", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，我為什麼要過這樣的日子！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我該是個有身份的人！我該在羽獸的鳴叫中醒來，喝一杯咖啡，然後去寫我的書稿......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼——女士們，我很抱歉，你們幫了我很多，可是......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請原諒我，請原諒我，我不該做這樣的事，我曾以我的道德自豪，我對我的傭人很好，每次在外面吃飯我都給雙倍的小費......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我堅持不住了，我真是受夠了，我不明白，我很困惑......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你可以放下手中的罐頭，然後離開這裡。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可以和你們交換！我有些薩爾貢的寶石，還有一把薩科塔的守護銃......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們用不上。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我求求你們，我求求你們——", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "false"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位先生抖得愈來愈厲害，最終雙膝一軟，跪在了地上。他大概從來沒有這麼哀求過別人，姿勢滑稽而可笑。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他緊緊地裹住自己的大衣，藏著肉罐頭的位置鼓出一塊，像是個寄居在身體上的悲哀腫瘤，又像是個備受愛惜的胎兒。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，先生，正門被封上了，你知道怎麼從陽台出去。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德！", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他走吧，讓他走吧！滾出這裡，帶著這個該死的罐頭，再也別回來！", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#3$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我很累，我不想再看到這些了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的......不想再看到這一切了。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "膽怯的市民慌亂地起身，他踉蹌著，猶豫著，彷彿不相信這位經營拳館的幫派分子就這麼放任自己離去。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戴菲恩憤怒地看著他，他別過頭，下意識地在身上摸索著。他什麼也沒有，鈔票和硬幣在現在的諾伯特區毫無用處。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chess"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位先生咬咬牙，把自己那支裝飾精美的鋼筆放在了地上，隨即轉身逃進黑暗裡。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他走了。", "name": "戴菲恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_866_1#6$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝爾德撿起鋼筆，隨手放進自己的口袋。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......戴菲恩。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們靠著，眯一會吧。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像那些日子，在影廳裡一樣。", "name": "貝爾德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_863_1#9$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g5_blockadewall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姑娘，聽說你是新被調來的雇傭兵？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......是的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你運氣不錯，這裡可是個輕鬆的任務。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要看著那些維多利亞佬別翻過封鎖線就行。要是有人敢鬧事，就幹掉他。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的！", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈！這幫傲慢自大的維多利亞人也該過過苦日子啦！要我說，不如再給他們幾把斧頭什麼的，他們自己就能把自己殺光了！", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......這好像不符合規定。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "丫頭，你真夠沒意思的。我們是薩卡茲，他們的死活和我們又有什麼關係？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如給自己找點樂子。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可......可是......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧，我去再睡一會，好好看住這裡。要是出了什麼意外，我也不介意連著你的那顆小腦袋瓜一起砍掉。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "300,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#10$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走了。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "channel": "n", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "n", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，姑娘。", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次我帶出來的東西不多，有些吃的，還有些藥......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "足夠了，謝謝，謝謝......", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是個薩卡茲，幫你應該沒什麼關係吧？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我們的同族......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老人家，也許我們可以去和長官們說一聲，你不用和那些維多利亞人待在一起。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不了，我在這裡生活了一輩子，這裡是我的家。", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#2$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在倫蒂尼姆？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡都有薩卡茲，不是嗎？在你們來倫蒂尼姆之後，我還當上了酒店經理呢......", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒去過卡茲戴爾，小姑娘，你是從那裡來的嗎？", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我也沒去過。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你的家是哪裡呢？", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家？我......我不清楚，我出生在哥倫比亞，可是......我以前的隊長說，卡茲戴爾才是我們薩卡茲的家。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#15$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你明明都沒去過那裡呀？", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我也不知道，但他們都這麼說......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我對那些士兵們宣揚的東西沒那麼感興趣，與其和他們一起殺人，我寧願想辦法修好酒店裡的那盞大吊燈。", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真該看看那盞吊燈還完好時候的樣子，要我說，沒有一位貴婦人的首飾能比得上！", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#6$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況，我年輕的時候，每天都要花好多功夫親手把它擦亮呢！", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......您還真是個奇怪的薩卡茲。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喜歡吊燈比喜歡殺人還要奇怪嗎？抱歉，我確實沒怎麼和雇傭兵打過交道......", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，有你這樣好心的姑娘為我帶些物資進來，我就已經心滿意足啦。", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再會吧，孩子，我不能在這裡待太久，如果以後有機會，你一定要來我的酒店看看。", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放在三四十年前，諾伯特區還熱鬧的時候，日落街酒店可是全倫蒂尼姆最好的住處！", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#11$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我會的。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許......等到打完這場仗？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#13$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_865_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，好，到時候我偷偷請你吃我們那裡最棒的甜品！", "name": "薩卡茲老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_865_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "25_mini02_victoria_street_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "破碎。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#3$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_3"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crystal_shatter", "channel": "s", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "s", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bottlebroken"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種咒術對於我們而言沒什麼意義，女妖。這些日子裡，你已經試了足夠多次了。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是浪費時間，你並不真正瞭解我們的集群。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#4$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的知識都是從學習中得來，但切身的經驗卻太少。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不然，暫且放下你那支骨筆如何？我們只是想和你散散步。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位我們曾化身的子爵先生說過，如今是這座城市最好的時節之一。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走慢些，中央區的這些行道樹可是倫蒂尼姆的驕傲。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變形者，你到底想為自己選擇何種命運？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有很多化身，你有很多變體，你以為自己總能逃過死亡。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會奏響你的挽歌，全部的你。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用這麼嚇唬人，女妖，我們清楚你有哪些手段。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，對於我們而言，個體的死亡不是終結，如同一座城市不會因某條街道的拆除而變質，一個文明不會因某行文字的消失而崩塌。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而文明亦會凋敝衰落。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我們重視更新，重視經驗。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們認識你的幾乎每一位先祖，女妖，他們都曾年輕過，都曾和你一樣懷有巨大的熱忱與希望。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許本應如此，或許變革本就該從挽歌中而生。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是他們最終都化為了一抔塵土。你們亦無法逃過背後的喪鐘。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的經驗依舊把你引向了那團毀滅的火焰身邊嗎？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是的。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經尋找了很多年，我們仍在尋找，以不同的樣子，在不同的地方。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是一位了不起的咒術大師。", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是否能邀請你，為這份長久的回憶提供些微不足道的佈景呢？", "name": "變形者集群"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_426_1#8$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......我曾在薩爾貢的沙海中沉淪百年，那是萬王之王的遠征剛剛結束的年月。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偉業尚未徹底淪為傳說之時，總是更讓人想要涉足。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女妖，縱使是幻境，吹起那些風沙吧。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耽誤你片刻微不足道的時間，與我尋找我的來路。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們沉入其中，讓我們一同跋涉。也許你會理解我，抑或我會認同你。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "證明給我看。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會有結論的，變形者。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帷幕。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#4$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_deserttownD", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，當然，這與我殘存記憶中的樣子有些出入，這不能怪你，風會刮走太多痕跡。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾在這裡為人們蓋房子，那時還沒有移動城市這種新奇玩意，石頭壘成的房屋最終也無非消散於風沙之間。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建起，再毀滅，建起，再毀滅......", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大多數人面對這種迴圈可能會感到疲憊，但那時我樂在其中。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你曾自比於文明，這是你所享受的“更新”嗎？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我並不享受。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那只是個潦草的比喻，文明終究會有其構建，有其結局。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我並不擁有這些，縱使我如此期冀。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是石頭，你是黃沙。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......黃沙。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，女妖，我是黃沙。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無可構建，已是結局。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不滿足於此。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_072", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾化為王酋的樣貌，面見過當時的那位萬王之王，他自稱“過去與未來之王”，萬事萬物的答案都在他的黃金寶庫之中。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問：陛下，我們身邊這一切的意義是什麼，您會把我們領向何方。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他高高昂起頭顱，向我聲稱：我的思索就是意義。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是那麼驕傲，那麼狂妄，他的身上灑滿午後的陽光，他相信自己是文明的主宰者。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我卻只看到，他滑稽地踩住了自己長袍的一角。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我感到無聊，於是我離開了那裡。", "name": "“薩爾貢人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_072"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g4_fogblockadestreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵們的手段讓我印象深刻。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這支小隊的人並不算少......然而你們潛入這裡簡直就像走入自家的後院一樣容易。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的那些快速牽引裝置，還有小型的幻術發生單元......難怪在薩卡茲如此嚴密的控制下，你們仍然能在倫蒂尼姆搭建自己的情報網。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#7$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乃至可以在倫蒂尼姆和這個被拋離的地塊之間來去自如。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#7$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞是這片大地上最強大的國家，而我效忠的那位公爵閣下又是維多利亞最值得被提及的一位。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們自然會給自己準備好各種技術手段。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "希望這些手段不會用在我們身上。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line362"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開斯特公爵對待她的朋友總是親切的。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "飛空艇就藏在這片地塊中的某個位置，據我們的估計，這裡應該有一座地下船塢。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更具體的情報呢？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#14$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就交給各位了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在老威靈頓和那位食腐者將軍試探出彼此的實力之前，你們還有一點時間，但恐怕也說不上多。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信各位最後能給我一個滿意的結果。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，這是場交易，亞歷山德莉娜殿下，還有羅德島的博士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}